title: VideoHive - Neon Music Visualizer Audio React
description:
With Neon Music Visualizer you can create realistic neon signs that react to your songs! The vivid colors and the audio reactive effect make your beats stand out. And if you want to go beyond the 4 pre-made templaes, with just a few simple shapes you can create your own unique visuals.

In addition you can easily achieve many different looks by adding images and details to your background, so it stays as fresh as your music. Or swap the colors for a completely new feeling.

Information: http://videohive.net/item/neon-music-visualizer-audio-react/14446438
